    "en": {
      "title": "Two weeks for the period given to deposit foreign currency",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Extending the general grace period granted for depositing or selling foreign currency to an authorized dealer (licensed commercial bank or National Savings Bank) to 26.07.2022, for a further period of 14 working days till 26.07.2022 The Minister of Finance has issued regulations under Section 8 of the Foreign Exchange Act No. 12 of 2017.",
        "For further details, the regulations under section 8 of the Foreign Exchange Act published in the Special Gazette No. 2287/16 dated 05.07.2022 can be consulted by downloading through www.dfe.lk."
      ],
